  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At the request of the Serbian Government, SDC will support three reforms on Serbia&#x2019;s path towards European integration: 1) the enforcement of a municipal finance law that awards good performance of local governments and ensures the necessary resources for democratic decisions, 2) the development of regional development policies for reducing regional disparities, including mechanisms for disaster risk prevention, and 3) high quality municipal audits aiming to achieve a rational use of public resources.</narrative>
